(11, 1, 'http://digitalica.pl/people', 'people - digitalica', 'people', '\n \n \n	\n	\n	\n	\n	\n        \n	 \n	\n	 \n\n	 \n         \n         \n	 \n        \n         \n         \n \n \n	\n		\n			digitalica \n			\n				   \n				   \n				   \n				   \n				   \n			 			\r\n				\r\n					 \r\n				 \r\n\r\n                                                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                                Aneta   \r\n                                                  Aneta Pertkiewicz Co-creator of digitalica in 2002, creative mind, currently living and working in London as digital/creative senior graphic designer. Life without cakes and chocolate is not for her, loves to take a pictures of everything and everywhere, likes far long journeys and loves quick, superfast bikes, works closely on creating portal enbike.co.uk . \r\n email: aneta@anetadesign.com                                          \r\n                                         \r\n                                     \r\n                                                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                                Local Hero   \r\n                                                 Local hero is a dj, producer, designer and organizer of club, art and cultural events. He is a member of DJ&rsquo;s group Urban Impulz Rec . He is experienced by wide range of music genres, starting from electronic and synthetic stuff, to dirty and overdriven guitar riffs.                                          \r\n                                         \r\n                                     \r\n                                                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                                Datasky   \r\n                                                 We Had a dream last night...  \r\n We had the same dream \r\n facebook                                           \r\n                                         \r\n                                     \r\n                                                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                                Shoo   \r\n                                                 Piotr, co-owner of kreujemy.to , currently living in Krakow, has been working as a graphic designer since 2006. His life is all about creativity, it does not matter if it\'s design, drawing or music production. Activity without creation is a waste of time. He loves to waste his time on traveling and getting to know local food.                                          \r\n                                         \r\n                                     \r\n                                                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                                WJTKR   \r\n                                                 Wojtek started his adventure with Digitalica Team in may 2003. Since  then, except a few kilos and years he\'s gained a quite big collection of  vinyl records, for which he digs on online shops and sales. At the  moment he wants to buy a the world\'s ugliest cat to discuss about Jason  Brooks illustrations. \r\n email: wojtker@gmail.com facebook: http://www.facebook.com/wojtekel                                           \r\n                                         \r\n                                     \r\n                                                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                                Bayerberg   \r\n                                                 Politicaly uncorect with eclectic taste of music nad drinks. Doing UiD/ UX by day and infographics by night. Well over a decade in design industry with half of than trying to hack my way through Londons creative circles one freelance gig at a time.  \r\n facebook: https://www.facebook.com/bayerberg.blog                                           \r\n                                         \r\n                                     \r\n                                                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                                                Tymon   \r\n                                                 Wojciech Zalot is 24 years old multidisciplinary designer specialized in digital production, interactive and typography based in Cracow, Poland.After 2 years he dropped college to push his knowledge and skills up in full-time work. Actually he is working as a full-time Lead Designer in Hand Made Flow and developing his own brand Rebeliarts from 2005 with his friends.His works was published in various magazines, websites and books, from over 2 years he is member of Keystone Design Union and represented in France byCreasenso. He had two individual exhibitions in last years and his works was also exhibited on many group galleries in different places.Combination of vivid colours, abstract shapes and photography is this what fully describes his style.Also inspired by artist like Adhemas Batista, Alex Trochut, Peter Jaworowski, Salvador Dali and many other different artists all over the world. \r\n Behance: http://www.behance.net/tymon                                           \r\n                                         \r\n                                     \r\n                                                                    \r\n                                        \r\n                                        \r\n                       