(29, 2, '2011-07-30', 'Smashin Tracks!', 'smashin-tracks', '<p>If you\'re looking for some good tunes to buy - this is a very interesting option. <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com" target="_blank" title="Smashin Tracks"><strong>SmashinTracks.com</strong></a> is the best place where you may buy and sell your own music, exclusive remixes and up to date unreleased tracks.</p>', '<p>If you\'re looking for some good tunes to buy - this is a very interesting option. <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/" target="_blank" title="Smashin Tracks"><strong>SmashinTracks.com</strong></a> is the best place where you may buy and sell your own music, exclusive remixes and up to date unreleased tracks.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>And this is what happened with our good friends, djs and producers from <strong><a href="http://www.urbanimpulz.com" target="_blank" title="Urban Impulz Rec.">Urban Impulz Rec.</a></strong> "After some intensive debates with people involved into new opened  SmashinTracks.com mp3 online shop, everybody from our Urban Impulz crew  decided to support the project.</p>\r\n<p><br /> So, from now on, if you\'re looking forward for some new releases  premiere, search them in Smashintracks.com. We do not abandon putting Urban Impulz tracks on Juno, but for sure it\'s going to be with some delays and  there\'s a possibility there are not going to be ful releases from people  involved with Urban Impulz Records. The newest tracks are available on SmashinTracks.com."</p>\r\n<p><span style="font-weight: bold;">- CJ REIGN</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/cj-reign">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/cj-reign </a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- MARTINO B</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/martino-b">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/martino-b</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- PROJECT JACK SPARROW</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/project-jack-sparrow">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/project-jack-sparrow</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- DR ORGAN</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/dr-organ">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/dr-organ</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- MADOGZ</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/madogz">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/madogz</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- SURANG</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/surang">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/surang</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- BASE CLUB</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/base-club">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/base-club</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- TACTICAL FUN</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/tactical-fun">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/tactical-fun</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- GREG SIN KEY</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/greg-sin-key">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/greg-sin-key</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- TOOFER</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/toofer">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/toofer</a><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">- NEFTI</span> - <a href="http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/nefti">http://www.smashintracks.com/profile/nefti</a></p>', 2, 1, 1, 0, 1),
